name: scoreboi - spooky scary vinyl
description: It's october. You know what it means. Scary skeletons dancing in cemeteries, werewolves and vampires going to work in their offices, just to come home late at night to listen to some Vinyls with good spooky songs. So if you are one of these creatures of the night that feels safe wandering in the streets in this part of the year, this vinyl is for you!
